ACT 1: SURVIVAL & DISCOVERY (Chapters 2-15)
ARC 1: "THE FRACTURED" (Learning the Basics)
Timeline: Weeks 1-4 Post-Collision
Story Beats:
Chapters 2-5: Figuring It Out
•	MC discovering his powers randomly activating
•	First accidental switch—wakes up somewhere else, doesn't remember
•	The Other leaves notes: "You're welcome for handling that. -Me"
•	Trying to survive in The Scar district (looting, avoiding military, hiding)
•	First Resolve encounter: Sees two Ruptured fighting, one's Core shatters
•	Realizes death is REAL here
Chapters 6-10: The Voice
•	MC and Other have their first real "conversation"
•	Establishing the Pact (version 1.0—vague and messy)
•	Inciting Incident: MC tries to stop a robbery, freezes up
•	Switch happens mid-confrontation
•	Other handles it brutally—thief is hospitalized
•	MC wakes up to consequences, terrified of himself
•	"This is why you'll never amount to anything. You're too weak."
Chapters 11-15: The Education
•	MC meets MENTOR FIGURE #1: An older Ruptured (maybe 40s)
•	Former construction worker, low-tier Resolve (Transmutation—can harden his skin)
•	Takes pity on MC, teaches him basics: 
o	Resolve Sense
o	Core protection
o	"Kid, you're leaking energy everywhere. You'll get yourself killed."
•	First training montage
•	Learning to feel his dual Cores
•	The Other is impatient: "This is taking too long!"
•	Arc climax: Mentor is killed by a Natural hunting Ruptured for sport
•	MC watches, powerless
•	The Other: "See? This is what happens when you're WEAK. No more running."
Arc 1 Theme: "You can't hide from power—learn it or die."
