ACT 4: UNIFICATION (Chapters 121-150+)
ARC 6: "THE WAR FOR RESOLVE"
Timeline: Months 7-8
Broad Strokes (You can expand):
•	All-out war between Ruptured and Naturals
•	MC becomes a symbol for the Ruptured ("proof that we're not mistakes")
•	The Predator becomes main antagonist (absorbing other Ruptured, getting stronger)
•	Climactic moment: MC's cores start to merge naturally through their shared conviction
•	Final battle: MC (unified) vs The Predator (bloated with stolen power)
•	Theme: Earned strength vs stolen strength
•	MC wins, but the world is forever changed
ARC 7: "WHAT COMES AFTER" (Epilogue arc)
•	Dealing with fame, responsibility
•	New threats emerging
•	MC fully unified, learning what it means to be complete
•	The Other: "So... am I gone now?"
•	Host: "No. You're just... me. We always were."
•	Setting up potential sequel hooks
