ACT 2: THE RESOLVER (Chapters 16-45)
ARC 2: "TRAINING GROUNDS" (Academy Arc)
Timeline: Month 2
The Resolver Program:
•	3-month intensive training for new Ruptured recruits
•	Mix of combat, Resolve theory, rescue operations, ethics
•	Structured like a police/military academy but for powered individuals
•	Located in a fortified compound outside the destroyed zones
Story Beats:
Chapters 16-20: The Rookies
•	MC meets his training squad (5-6 recruits): 
o	Hothead guy - Enforcement type, reckless, wants to prove himself
o	Tactical girl - Projection type, smart, competitive with MC
o	Gentle giant - Transmutation type, doesn't want to fight but has to
o	Mysterious quiet one - Denial type, has a dark past
