✓ Complete, natural sentences ✓ Personality shows through dialogue (Other is blunt, confident, impatient / MC is cautious, analytical, empathetic) ✓ They argue like people who know each other TOO well ✓ Banter and bickering are constant ✓ Genuine moments of understanding mixed in ✓ They finish each other's thoughts during sync moments ✓ Neither is "dumb" - both are intelligent, just different approaches
