Key Scene (Chapter 96):
After mission, sitting on rooftop.

Hana: "Can I ask you something?"

MC: "Sure."

Hana: "When you unify... will the Other disappear?"

MC: "...I don't know. Maybe."

Hana: "Does that scare you?"

MC: "Yeah. He's... he's me. But he's also his own person. I don't want to erase him."

Other: "...I don't want to disappear either."

MC: (internally) Then we'll find another way.

Hana: "Whatever happens, I'm here. Both of you."

MC: "...Thank you."

She takes his hand.

Other: "Okay, now kiss her."

MC: (internally) I WILL KILL YOU.

Other: "You can't kill me without killing yourself, genius."

Hana: "He just said something, didn't he?"

MC: "...Yeah."

Hana: (laughing) "You two are adorable."
