Chapters 101-110: The Architects
•	Conspiracy revealed (same as before)
•	Final preparation for war
•	MC calls his mom
Reconciliation Scene (Chapter 105):
MC alone in his apartment room. Phone in hand.

Other: "You should call her."

MC: "After everything—"

Other: "We might die. Do you want that to be how it ends?"

MC: "...No."

He dials.

Mom: "...Hello?"

MC: "Mom. It's me."

Silence. Then crying.

Mom: "Oh god. Oh god, you're alive."

MC: "Yeah. I'm... I'm okay."

Mom: "I saw the news. The Resolvers. Are you—"

MC: "Yeah. I'm one of them."

Mom: "I'm so sorry. For everything. For Reina, for—"

MC: "I know. I'm sorry too. For cutting you off."

Mom: "Are you safe?"

MC: "...As safe as I can be."

Mom: "Promise me you'll come back."

MC: "I promise."

He hangs up. Wipes his eyes.

Other: "Feel better?"

MC: "...Yeah. Actually, yeah."
________________________________________
Chapters 111-120: Final Battle
•	vs Predator (full power)
•	MC's cores synchronize
•	Unification happens
•	The Other's final words:
Mid-battle. Cores merging.

Other: "Hey. Before we—"

MC: "Don't. Don't say goodbye."

Other: "I'm not. I'm saying... thanks."

MC: "For what?"

Other: "For not hating me. For listening. For giving a shit."

MC: "You're me. How could I hate you?"

Other: "Lots of people hate themselves."

MC: "...Yeah. But not anymore."

Other: "We did good, right? We matter now."

MC: "Yeah. We matter."

The merge completes. Single consciousness.

MC (unified): "We always did."
________________________________________
Epilogue:
•	MC promoted to Captain
•	Squad still together (some in his new division)
•	Apartment life continues (Kaito + Sara + now Hana visits)
•	Reina: Still detained, but MC visits sometimes 
o	"I'll wait for you. However long it takes."
•	Mom: Regular calls now
•	MC content, purposeful, HOME
Final scene:
MC on the apartment balcony.

Hana: "What are you thinking about?"

MC: "Everything. Where I was. Where I am now."

Hana: "Regrets?"

MC: "...No. Not anymore."

Kaito yells from inside: "Dinner's ready! Get in here!"

Sara: "If you two are making out, at least close the door!"

MC: (laughing) "Coming!"

He looks at his reflection. Single person. Complete.

MC: (internally) We made it.

The voice is his own now. Unified.

He smiles.

Fade out.
