CHARACTER LIST - COMPLETE ROSTER
________________________________________
MAIN CAST
PROTAGONIST:
MC (Male, 21)
•	Dual Resolve cores (Denial + Enforcement types)
•	Split personality: Host + The Other
•	Former college dropout, dead-end jobs
•	Quarter-life crisis, loneliness issues
•	Arc: Isolation → Connection → Wholeness
THE OTHER (MC's second personality)
•	Shares MC's body, can take control
•	Offensive/instinctive fighter
•	Blunt, confident, reckless
•	Arc: Rage → Partnership → Unity with Host
________________________________________
DIVISION 7 (Core Team - 7 People)
