MC NAME - MORE UNIQUE OPTIONS
________________________________________
BETTER MC NAME OPTIONS:
OPTION 1: SORA KURODA (黒田 空)
•	Sora = "sky/emptiness" (reflects his internal void, wanting to fill it)
•	Kuroda = "black rice field" (humble/dark origins)
•	Vibe: Not too common, has depth, sounds good in action scenes
OPTION 2: TETSU MIKAGE (御影 哲)
•	Tetsu = "philosophy/wisdom" (ironic for someone at war with himself)
•	Mikage = "shadow/reflection" (literal split personality theme)
•	Vibe: Sophisticated, uncommon, thematic
OPTION 3: RYO KAMIYA (神谷 涼)
•	Ryo = "cool/refreshing" (surface calm hiding internal chaos)
•	Kamiya = "god valley" (seeking something higher/greater)
•	Vibe: Strong, simple, memorable
OPTION 4: KENJI SHIZUKA (静 賢二)
•	Kenji = "wise second son" (fitting for someone with two sides)
•	Shizuka = "quiet/calm" (ironic—he's anything but internally)
•	Vibe: Subtle, layered meaning
OPTION 5: ASAHI TATSUMI (辰巳 朝日)
•	Asahi = "morning sun" (new beginning, rising from darkness)
•	Tatsumi = "dragon snake" (duality, two powerful forces)
•	Vibe: Dynamic, less common, strong imagery
OPTION 6: JIN MURASAKI (紫 迅)
•	Jin = "swift/fast" (constant switching, rapid changes)
•	Murasaki = "purple" (mixing red and blue—two halves making one)
•	Vibe: Cool, uncommon surname, color symbolism
MY TOP RECOMMENDATION: TETSU MIKAGE
•	"Shadow/reflection" surname is PERFECT for split personality
•	Tetsu sounds strong but not generic
•	Not overused in anime/manga
•	Good for nickname potential ("Tetsu" or "Mikage")
ALTERNATE: RYO KAMIYA
•	Simpler, punchier
•	"God valley" implies reaching for something greater
•	Easy to remember, strong sound
