AYUMI REDESIGN - INSANE POWERHOUSE
NEW CONCEPT: AYUMI TANAKA - "THE ANOMALY"
BASIC INFO:
•	Female, 22
•	Grade: A+ (borderline S-rank)
•	International Resolver from German division (half-Japanese, half-German)
•	Dominion type - but EXTREME application
•	Personality: Choso/Naoya hybrid energy 
o	Obsessive, intense, slightly unhinged
o	Brutal in combat (Naoya's viciousness)
o	Devoted to those she accepts (Choso's loyalty)
o	Zero chill, maximum intensity
________________________________________
ABILITY: "ABSOLUTE DOMAIN"
How it works:
•	Creates a territory where she has TOTAL authority
•	Within her Domain (15-20 meter radius): 
o	Can enforce "rules" on reality itself
o	"No violence against me" = attacks literally stop
o	"You will tell the truth" = compelled honesty
o	"Pain is amplified" = agony for enemies
o	Basically mini-reality warping within her zone
Limitations:
•	Insanely draining (can only maintain 3-5 minutes max)
•	Smaller Domain = stronger rules, larger = weaker
•	Can only enforce 2-3 rules simultaneously
•	After it drops, she's vulnerable for 30 seconds
•	Doesn't work on S-rank opponents (their conviction overpowers hers)
Why she's borderline S-rank:
•	Inside her Domain, she's UNTOUCHABLE by A-rank and below
•	Can 1v5 easily within her zone
•	But limited duration and vulnerability window keep her from true S-rank
•	Basically a "glass cannon god mode" build
________________________________________
PERSONALITY - THE INSANITY:
Combat:
•	Violently efficient - doesn't play with opponents
•	"Why waste time? Just die already."
•	Laughs during intense fights (not sadistically, just... genuinely excited)
•	Gets ANGRY when opponents don't take her seriously
•	"You're holding back? That's insulting."
Relationships:
•	Extremely selective - most people annoy her
•	Once she accepts you, she's RIDE OR DIE (Choso energy)
•	Possessive of her "people"
•	"Touch my team and I'll erase you from existence."
With Tetsu/MC:
•	Fascinated by his dual nature from first meeting
•	"You're two people? That's so unfair. I want that."
•	Intensely curious about how The Other works
•	Flirts by threatening him
•	"I could crush you. But I won't. That means I like you."
•	The Other is equally fascinated: "She's insane. I love it."
•	Host: "Please stop encouraging her."
Quirks:
•	Doesn't understand "normal" social cues
•	Says exactly what she thinks (zero filter)
•	Eats like a monster (burns insane calories from Domain usage)
•	Sleeps 12+ hours after missions (complete crash)
•	Collects weapons from defeated opponents (trophy habit)
•	Speaks German when extremely angry
________________________________________
BACKSTORY SKETCH:
•	Father: High-ranking German Resolver (Natural, A-rank)
•	Mother: Japanese Resolver (Natural, B-rank)
•	Awakened Resolve at age 8 (prodigy, terrifyingly young)
•	Her Domain manifested during a hostage situation
•	Accidentally killed the hostage-takers by enforcing "Stop breathing" as a rule
•	Traumatized her parents, but she was... fine?
•	"They were going to hurt people. I stopped them. What's the problem?"
•	Raised as a weapon by European Resolvers
•	No childhood, just training
•	Sees combat as "the only honest thing"
•	Joins international task force because "I was bored"
________________________________________
ROLE IN STORY:
Introduction (International Arc, Ch 74):
•	First meeting: She casually defeats 3 A-rank Architects agents solo
•	Team watches in horror/awe
•	Tetsu: "Who the hell is that?"
•	Ayumi (blood-spattered, smiling): "Ayumi Tanaka. You're the split-core everyone's talking about, right? Show me."
•	Activates Domain
•	"Fight me. I want to see if you're interesting."
•	Tetsu forced to switch between Host/Other mid-fight just to keep up
•	She LOVES it
•	"You're fun! Let's be friends."
•	Kaito (whispering): "That's not how friendship works..."
Development:
•	Initially treats Tetsu as "interesting specimen"
•	Slowly develops actual feelings (doesn't understand them at first)
•	"Why do I want to protect you? This is annoying."
•	Becomes fiercely protective of Division 7
•	"They're MY idiots now. Back off."
Combat Role:
•	Ace in the hole for impossible situations
•	When she activates Domain, enemies panic
•	"Oh fuck, it's the Anomaly. RUN."
•	Takes on multiple high-tiers solo during final battles
Romance:
•	Slow burn but INTENSE
•	She makes the first move (aggressively)
•	"I've decided. You're mine now."
•	Tetsu: "Don't I get a say?"
•	Ayumi: "No."
•	The Other: "I like her."
•	Actually vulnerable around him (rare)
•	Post-battle scene: exhausted, drops her mask
•	"Don't... look at me like this. I'm supposed to be strong."
•	Tetsu: "You are strong. You're also human."
•	She cries for the first time in years
________________________________________
POWER SCALING:
Domain Active: Can fight S-rank for brief periods (wins vs A-rank easily) Domain Down: High B-rank in raw combat Strategic Value: SS-rank (her Domain can turn impossible fights winnable)
Why not full S-rank:
•	Time limit is crippling
•	Vulnerability window is exploitable
•	S-ranks can overpower her rules through sheer conviction
•	She's a tactical nuke, not sustained firepower
