TRANSMUTATION REPLACEMENT
NEW TYPE: CONVERSION
One-liner: "Transforming one form of energy or matter into another"
How it's DIFFERENT from Tokyo Ghoul:
Tokyo Ghoul's Kagune: Biological transformation, body parts into weapons Conversion: Energy/matter alchemy, not body-horror
________________________________________
CONVERSION TYPE USERS:
DAICHI YAMAMOTO (revised):
•	Ability: "Life Exchange"
•	Converts his Resolve energy directly into healing
•	Can also reverse it—convert vitality INTO Resolve (dangerous)
•	Touches wounded ally → injury transfers to him → he converts it to dissipating energy
•	"I turn damage into nothing. That's my job."
•	NOT shapeshifting, purely energy conversion
REINA HAYASHI/KITAGAWA (revised):
•	Ability: "Apex Shift" (Kitagawa bloodline)
•	Converts her body's state between forms (solid/liquid/energy)
•	Can become living metal (defense), flowing water (evasion), or pure energy (offense)
•	NOT "growing tentacles" or "body horror"
•	More like state-of-matter manipulation
•	Example: Turns arm to steel for blocking, shifts to water to dodge, reforms as energy blade
•	Ancestral technique passed down in Natural families
________________________________________
UPDATED TYPE LIST:
1.	ENFORCEMENT - Force imposition
2.	DENIAL - Reality rejection
3.	PROJECTION - Construct creation
4.	DOMINION - Authority/control
5.	CONVERSION - Energy/matter transformation (replaces Transmutation)
