VOID - FULL DEVELOPMENT
KENTO "VOID" MORI - PRIMARY ANTAGONIST (Acts 2-3)
BASIC INFO:
•	Male, 27
•	Former Resolver (A-rank before he went rogue)
•	Current Grade: S-rank (through absorption)
•	Unique ability type (corrupted Denial)
________________________________________
ABILITY: "CONSUMPTION"
How it works:
•	Can absorb Cores from dying Ruptured
•	Experiences their final moments/memories
•	Gains fragments of their abilities temporarily
•	Each absorption temporarily boosts his power
•	The addiction: Feeling someone's life energy fade is euphoric to him
•	"It's the only time I feel REAL."
Mechanics:
•	Must be present when Core shatters
•	Absorbs the dissipating Resolve energy
•	Gains victim's ability for 24-48 hours (then fades)
•	Can store up to 5 abilities simultaneously
•	Cost: Slowly losing his original personality (fragmented by memories)
Current Arsenal (by time MC meets him):
•	Base: Denial type (his original)
•	+4 absorbed abilities from previous victims
•	Becomes more dangerous over time
________________________________________
PERSONALITY - TRAGIC VILLAIN:
Surface:
•	Nihilistic, philosophical
•	Speaks in metaphors
•	Calm, almost serene
•	"We're all just energy waiting to dissipate."
Underneath:
•	Desperately afraid of feeling empty
•	Addicted to the "high" of absorption
•	Knows he's becoming a monster
•	Can't stop
•	"I don't want to do this. But I NEED to."
Quirks:
•	Talks to the "voices" (absorbed victims' memories)
•	Sometimes switches personalities mid-conversation
•	"Sorry, that was Takeshi speaking. He's still angry."
•	Draws portraits of his victims (guilt manifestation)
•	Keeps a journal of their last thoughts
•	Wants someone to stop him but refuses to stop himself
________________________________________
BACKSTORY:
Pre-Collision:
•	Promising young Resolver
•	Denial-type, specialized in protecting others
•	Engaged to another Resolver
•	"I'll keep you safe. Always."
During Collision:
•	He and his fiancée caught in the wave
•	She was dying, Core failing
•	In desperation, he tried to "take her pain"
•	Accidentally absorbed her dying Core
•	Felt her death from the inside
•	The euphoria was OVERWHELMING
•	She died in his arms
•	He felt more alive than ever
•	Hated himself for it
After:
•	Tried to resist the urge
•	But the emptiness was unbearable
•	"I'm hollow without it."
•	Started "mercy killing" Ruptured who were dying anyway
•	Justified it: "I'm ending their suffering."
•	Escalated to hunting stable Ruptured
•	"They'll die eventually. I'm just... accelerating it."
•	Went completely rogue 4 months post-Collision
________________________________________
ROLE IN STORY:
First Encounter (Ch 40 - End of Field Work Arc):
•	Division 7 investigating disappearances
•	Find Void standing over a fresh victim
•	Tetsu: "Who are you?"
•	Void: "Someone who understands you."
•	"You're two people in one body. I'm... everyone I've consumed. We're the same."
•	Major fight
•	Void nearly kills Mitsuki (absorbs her Resolve partially, she survives but weakened)
•	Captain Takeshi intervenes
•	Void escapes
•	"I'll be back for you, Tetsu. Your dual cores... I wonder what they taste like."
Recurring Threat (Acts 2-3):
•	Hunts Tetsu specifically
•	Sees the dual cores as "the ultimate high"
•	"Two complete personalities in one soul? If I absorb you, I'll finally be WHOLE."
•	Multiple encounters throughout international arc
•	Each time, he's stronger (more absorbed abilities)
•	Each time, more fragmented personality
Climax Fight (Ch 85-88):
•	Before final Architect battle
•	Void ambushes Tetsu (now has 12+ absorbed abilities)
•	"I've saved you for last. My magnum opus."
•	Mirror fight: Void switches between absorbed abilities, Tetsu switches between Host/Other
•	Both are fragmented beings seeking wholeness
Resolution:
•	Tetsu's cores begin resonating
•	Void: "How? How are you UNIFYING? I've consumed dozens and I'm still EMPTY!"
•	Tetsu: "Because I accept both sides of myself. You're trying to become everyone else."
•	Void breaks down
•	"I just... I just wanted to feel her again. Just once."
•	Tetsu offers mercy kill
•	"I can end it. No more suffering."
•	Void: "...Thank you."
•	Tetsu absorbs Void's Resolve (first and only time he does this)
•	Experiences Void's final memory: his fiancée smiling
•	"It's okay. You can rest now."
•	Void dies peacefully
Impact:
•	Tetsu temporarily gains Consumption ability
•	Uses it to sense The Architects' locations (absorbed Cores have memories)
•	Ability fades after 24 hours
•	Character growth: Mercy can be just as hard as violence
________________________________________
THEMATIC ROLE:
Tetsu vs Void:
•	Both fragmented beings
•	Tetsu seeks unity WITHIN
•	Void seeks unity by CONSUMING others
•	"You complete yourself. I complete myself with others."
•	Shows what Tetsu COULD become if he went wrong path
