MC NAME - FINAL OPTIONS ROUND
________________________________________
MORE UNIQUE OPTIONS:
OPTION 1: TETSU MIKAGE (黒田 哲) (Your observation)
•	Why it works: Instant recall, "shadow/reflection" = perfect for split personality
•	Sounds strong, not generic, thematic depth
•	Nickname potential: "Tetsu" (casual), "Mikage" (formal/enemies)
OPTION 2: RYO KAMIYA (神谷 涼) (You liked this)
•	Strong, simple, memorable
•	"God valley" + "cool/calm" = ironic contrast to internal chaos
•	Nickname potential: "Ryo" flows well in dialogue
OPTION 3: SHUN ARIMA (有馬 駿)
•	Shun = "speed/excellence" (constant switching between personalities)
•	Arima = "exists/has horse" (philosophical—questioning existence)
•	Vibe: Sophisticated, uncommon, literary feel
OPTION 4: KAZUKI IBUKI (伊吹 一樹)
•	Kazuki = "one tree/harmony" (two halves, one whole)
•	Ibuki = "breath" (life force, resolve energy metaphor)
•	Vibe: Poetic, layered meaning, strong sound
OPTION 5: YUUTO SAGARA (相良 悠斗)
•	Yuuto = "gentle person/distant fighter" (Host vs Other duality)
•	Sagara = "mutual good" (two sides working together)
•	Vibe: Smooth, easy to say, optimistic undertones
OPTION 6: DAIKI KIRIGAYA (桐ヶ谷 大輝)
•	Daiki = "great radiance/great nobility" (ambition to matter)
•	Kirigaya = "paulownia valley" (rare tree, hidden potential)
•	Vibe: Grand, aspirational, fantasy-lite feel
OPTION 7: ITSUKI MINASE (皆瀬 樹)
•	Itsuki = "tree" (rooted but wanting to grow)
•	Minase = "everyone's rapids" (caught in the flow of others' expectations)
•	Vibe: Grounded, relatable, slightly melancholic
________________________________________
MY RANKINGS:
TIER S (Best):
1.	TETSU MIKAGE - Thematically perfect, instantly memorable
2.	RYO KAMIYA - Clean, strong, easy to remember
TIER A (Great): 3. SHUN ARIMA - Sophisticated, literary 4. KAZUKI IBUKI - Poetic, meaningful
TIER B (Good but less impactful): 5. Yuuto Sagara 6. Daiki Kirigaya
7. Itsuki Minase
