FINAL RECOMMENDATION:
Go with TETSU MIKAGE if you want:
•	Instant thematic connection (shadow/reflection)
•	Strong, memorable sound
•	Perfect for merchandise/branding ("Mikage" looks cool written)
Go with RYO KAMIYA if you want:
•	Cleaner, simpler feel
•	More grounded/"normal guy" vibe
•	Easier for international audiences
Both work perfectly. Tetsu has more thematic weight, Ryo has more accessibility.
