1. THE KITAGAWA FAMILY BLOODLINE (Reina's Adoptive Family)
KITAGAWA CLAN - ANCIENT NATURAL LINEAGE
History:
•	One of the oldest Resolve-using families in Japan (400+ years)
•	Operated as shadow protectors of imperial family during feudal era
•	Transitioned to corporate power in modern era
•	Own massive conglomerate (tech, pharmaceuticals, private security)
Bloodline Ability: "DUAL NATURE"
•	Inherited ability to use TWO Resolve types
•	Typically Conversion + one other type
•	Extremely rare—only direct bloodline members
•	Manifests around age 10-12
Current Head:
•	MASATO KITAGAWA (Male, 52, S-rank Natural)
•	Conversion + Projection hybrid
•	Cold, calculating businessman
•	Sees Reina as "investment" not daughter
•	"We paid for perfection. You will BE perfect."
Why They Adopted Reina:
•	Scouts identified her as high-potential Ruptured
•	Wanted to study/control a Ruptured with their bloodline training
•	"If we can mold a Ruptured into our standards, imagine the possibilities."
•	Essentially bought her from Keiko (MC's mom) for ¥50 million
•	Keiko was desperate, thought Reina would have better life
•	She was wrong
Reina's Treatment:
•	Trained since age 9, no childhood
•	Daily combat drills, Resolve conditioning
•	Emotional suppression training
•	"Feelings make you weak. Excise them."
•	Other Kitagawa members treat her as "the project"
•	Only acknowledged when she succeeds
•	Became Grade A by age 16 (youngest ever)
Family Dynamics:
•	Reina has "siblings" (other Kitagawa children)
•	They resent her (outsider with family name)
•	Constant competition, sabotage attempts
•	She's isolated even in her "family"
•	Only memory of real family: Tetsu
