2. THE ORIGINAL GRADE-S FIGHTERS - DETAILED LORE
"THE FRACTURED ONE" - Full Story
Real Name: UNKNOWN (records destroyed by Architects) Codename: "Zenith" Grade: S+ rank
Background:
•	Born with split personality naturally (pre-Collision, extremely rare)
•	Two complete consciousnesses from birth
•	Parents thought they were "possessed"
•	Awakened Resolve at age 15 (both personalities manifested separate types)
•	Spent 20 years mastering unification
•	By age 35, achieved perfect synchronization
•	Became most powerful Resolve user in history
Why They Were Dangerous:
•	Discovered the truth: Architects had been manipulating governments for centuries
•	Planned to expose Resolve existence to the world
•	"Humanity deserves to know. Secrecy breeds corruption."
•	Gathered evidence, prepared global broadcast
•	The Architects couldn't allow it
The Assassination:
•	Sent "The Arbiter" to eliminate them
•	Fight lasted 6 hours
•	Destroyed entire district (became Ground Zero)
•	Fractured One realized they couldn't win
•	Made a choice: Scatter their unified Resolve
•	"If I can't free them with truth, I'll free them with power."
•	Deliberately shattered their Core during the fight
•	Energy wave infected thousands → created the Ruptured
•	Died to give others what they had: Resolve
Legacy:
•	Fragments of their Resolve live in all Ruptured
•	Split-core Ruptured have LARGER fragments
•	Tetsu has one of the most complete fragments
•	If all fragments reunited: Fractured One could theoretically resurrect
