________________________________________
RENAME OPTIONS:
OPTION 1: THE COVENANT
•	Implies sacred agreement/ancient pact
•	"We are bound by covenant to protect humanity"
•	Members = Covenant Keepers
•	Weight: Religious/historical gravitas
OPTION 2: THE TRIBUNAL
•	Judge/jury/executioner energy
•	"The Tribunal has passed judgment"
•	Members = Arbiters (ties to "The Arbiter" character)
•	Weight: Authority, finality
OPTION 3: THE ORTHODOXY
•	"True/correct belief" system
•	Implies they're the "pure" Naturals
•	Members = Orthodoxists or High Clerics
•	Weight: Religious fanaticism, old power
OPTION 4: THE SANCTUM
•	Hidden holy place
•	"The Sanctum has stood for centuries"
•	Members = Sanctum Lords/Ladies
•	Weight: Mystery, untouchable power
OPTION 5: THE PRIMACY
•	"First/original" - they were first Resolve users
•	Implies natural hierarchy
•	Members = Primals or First Blood
•	Weight: Evolutionary superiority complex
OPTION 6: THE ECLIPSE
