like some have unique powers like natural elements (fire , water , rtc)... some projections , some high reactive speed (like naoya zenin)... (even like chosso)... some with resolved weapon bearers .. also i have thought of this idea where the other self of tetsu -- to make him like get seperated from tetsu himself and the other self realises that being good , doing all good to everyone brought no peace and good feeling for tetsu overall hence , he decides to go on his path ... opposite of tetsu which is against him and against him everyone... because tetsu at the beginning of the story always believed and wanted to live a insane life even if it's for a day no matter the path
POWER SYSTEM OVERHAUL + THE OTHER'S SEPARATION
________________________________________
PART 1: NEW RESOLVE SYSTEM - "MANIFESTATION TYPES"
CORE CONCEPT:
Resolve = Your core conviction externalized as power
Instead of 5 rigid types, Resolve manifests in PERSONAL ways based on:
1.	Your deepest belief/conviction
2.	Your personality/nature
3.	How you VIEW power itself
Result: Every user is UNIQUE, but patterns emerge
________________________________________
MANIFESTATION CATEGORIES (Not Types - Looser):
CATEGORY 1: ELEMENTAL MANIFESTATION
"My will takes the form of natural force"
How it works:
•	Your Resolve embodies an element (fire, water, ice, lightning, wind, earth, etc.)
•	NOT "elemental magic" - it's YOUR CONVICTION given elemental form
•	Element reflects personality/belief
Examples:
KAITO NOMURA - FIRE MANIFESTATION
•	Conviction: "I burn brighter the more I fight for others"
•	Resolve manifests as crimson flames
•	Gets hotter when protecting teammates
•	Signature move: "Blazing Heart" - flame armor that damages attackers
•	Weapon: Doesn't use one (pure elemental brawler)
SARA FUJIMOTO - LIGHTNING MANIFESTATION
•	Conviction: "I strike with precision and inevitability"
•	Resolve manifests as controlled lightning
•	Tactical, calculated strikes
•	Signature move: "Heaven's Verdict" - delayed lightning marks that detonate on command
•	Weapon: Conductive wire she weaves into traps/constraints
MITSUKI TANAKA - WIND MANIFESTATION
•	Conviction: "I sense everything; nothing escapes me"
•	Resolve manifests as sensory wind currents
•	Detects movement, breathing, heartbeats through air pressure
•	Signature move: "Whisper Net" - creates invisible wind field that reports all movement
•	Weapon: Doesn't fight directly (pure support/scout)
________________________________________
CATEGORY 2: WEAPON MANIFESTATION
"My will takes the form of a weapon/tool"
How it works:
•	Resolve crystallizes as a physical weapon
•	Weapon reflects how you VIEW conflict
•	Can be summoned/dismissed
•	Grows with user
Examples:
AYUMI TANAKA - DOMAIN WEAPON: "THRONE OF ABSOLUTES"
•	Conviction: "Within my domain, my word is law"
•	Doesn't manifest a handheld weapon
•	Manifests a THRONE that appears behind her when she activates Domain
•	Sitting on it = Domain active (15m radius of absolute authority)
•	Standing = Domain inactive but Throne can be used as shield/platform
•	Grade 1 bordering 0
DAICHI YAMAMOTO - HEALING HANDS: "SANCTUARY PALMS"
•	Conviction: "I transform suffering into peace"
•	Manifests as golden energy around his hands
•	Can touch wounds and convert damage into dissipating light
•	Can reverse it: convert his vitality into explosive energy (desperation move)
•	Weapon type but not for combat
REN TAKAHASHI - TACTICAL WEB: "SPIDER'S THEOREM"
•	Conviction: "I control the battlefield through perfect positioning"
•	Manifests as invisible energy threads
•	Lays complex trap networks across combat zones
•	Can pull, restrict, redirect movement
•	Signature move: Manipulates ally and enemy positions like chess pieces
________________________________________
CATEGORY 3: BODY ENHANCEMENT
"My will enhances my physical form"
How it works:
•	Resolve amplifies body capabilities
•	Speed, strength, durability, reflexes
•	Different users enhance different aspects
Examples:
NAOYA-STYLE SPEED USER - [NEW CHARACTER: SHINJI HAYATE]
•	Conviction: "Victory goes to the fastest"
•	Grade 2 Resolver, rival introduced during training
•	Manifests as REACTIVE SPEED
•	Moves faster the longer a fight continues (builds momentum)
•	After 24 seconds of combat: near-teleportation speed
•	Weakness: Reset if he stops moving for 3+ seconds
•	Personality: Arrogant speedster, looks down on "slow" fighters
•	Clashes with Tetsu (calls him "the indecisive one")
JIRO SAITO - IMMOVABLE FORCE
•	Conviction: "I am the wall nothing breaks"
•	Manifests as supernatural durability
•	Can tank attacks that would kill others
•	Gets STRONGER when protecting someone behind him
•	No weapon - pure defensive body enhancement
REINA KITAGAWA - APEX PREDATOR
•	Conviction: "I am evolution's answer to any threat"
•	Manifests as STATE SHIFTING (solid/liquid/energy forms)
•	Becomes living metal (defense), flowing water (evasion), pure energy (offense)
•	Kitagawa Lineage: Also has minor elemental control (ice manipulation)
•	Dual manifestation makes her Grade 1 borderline 0
________________________________________
