Examples:
CAPTAIN TAKESHI KUROSAWA - "SENTINEL CONSTRUCTS"
•	Conviction: "I create fortresses that protect my people"
•	Manifests massive defensive structures
•	Walls, barriers, bunkers appear from thin air
•	Can also create giant warrior constructs (humanoid defenders)
•	Kurosawa Lineage: Constructs last longer than normal
CHOSO-STYLE BLOOD USER - [NEW CHARACTER: AKANE TSUKISHIMA]
•	Conviction: "My life is my weapon; I bleed to win"
•	Grade 2 Resolver, introduced during field missions
•	Manifests as BLOOD MANIPULATION
•	Can weaponize her own blood (blades, projectiles, shields)
•	Stronger when injured (more blood available)
•	Personality: Calm, analytical, sees combat as equation
•	"Every drop I lose is a weapon I gain"
•	Forms temporary alliance with Division 7
