"My will defies categorization"
Examples:
KENTO "VOID" MORI - CONSUMPTION
•	Conviction: "I become whole by absorbing others"
•	Corrupted sensory ability (Mori Lineage gone wrong)
•	Absorbs dying Cores, gains temporary abilities
•	Currently has: Fire element, Speed enhancement, Blade manifestation, Shadow manipulation, + his base denial ability
•	Grade 1 - becomes stronger with each absorption
TETSU MIKAGE - DUAL CORE SYSTEM
•	Two separate manifestations:
HOST (Blue Core):
•	Conviction: "I see all outcomes; I choose the right path"
•	FORESIGHT MANIFESTATION - "CONSEQUENCE MAPPING"
•	Can see 3-5 seconds into immediate future (like precognition)
•	Shows him attack trajectories, enemy movements, consequences
•	Creates blue holographic "prediction lines" he can see
•	Weakness: Information overload, paralysis by analysis
•	No weapon - pure tactical ability
THE OTHER (Red Core):
•	Conviction: "I seize victory through overwhelming will"
•	MOMENTUM MANIFESTATION - "RELENTLESS SURGE"
•	Every attack builds kinetic energy
•	First punch = normal. Fifth punch = devastating. Tenth = catastrophic
•	Momentum carries between rapid strikes
•	Weapon: Crimson energy blade that extends from his forearm (like a bracer-sword hybrid)
•	Weakness: Resets if he stops attacking for 5+ seconds
UNIFIED (Purple Core - Late Game):
•	Both abilities simultaneously
•	Predicts with Host's Foresight, executes with Other's Momentum
•	Perfect combat style
