•	Different goals, different methods
•	But same origin, same core
•	Brothers, not halves
Final Scene (Epilogue):
Tetsu on apartment balcony.

Akatsuki appears (visits sometimes).

Akatsuki: "Heard you made Captain. Proud of you."

Tetsu: "You took down that trafficking ring. Proud of you too."

Akatsuki: "We're both living now. Just differently."

Tetsu: "Yeah. Finally."

Akatsuki: "You think we'd be stronger merged?"

Tetsu: "Probably."

Akatsuki: "But happier?"

Tetsu: "...No. This is better."

Akatsuki: "Agreed."

They sit in silence. Two people who used to be one.

Both finally complete.

Fade out.
