WHY THIS WORKS:
✅ Subverts expectation - Unification ISN'T the answer ✅ Character growth - Both learn they're better apart ✅ Thematic depth - "Wholeness ≠ Unity" ✅ Unique twist - Most stories unite split characters; yours separates them ✅ Realistic - Sometimes growth means diverging, not merging ✅ Satisfying - Both get what they want (hero path + free path)
