CHARACTER ROSTER - DETAILED
________________________________________
1. ELEMENTAL USER - "INFERNUS"
BASIC INFO:
Name: RYO KAGEYAMA (影山 涼) Age: 26 Grade: 2 (borderline 1) Affiliation: International Resolver (Russian Division, transferred to Japan)
APPEARANCE:
•	Tall, lean, burn scars covering left side of face and neck
•	White hair (naturally black, burned white from his own flames)
•	Always smoking (cigarette never goes out - lit by his Resolve)
•	Wears heavy coat even in summer (fire-resistant material)
•	Eyes: One brown (right), one red (left - damaged by fire)
•	VISUAL HOOK: Smoke constantly rising from his body when agitated
RESOLVE MANIFESTATION: "PURGATORY FLAME"
Conviction: "I am the fire that purifies through destruction"
How it works:
•	Manifests BLACK FLAMES (hotter than normal fire, doesn't go out easily)
•	Can control existing fires + create new ones
•	Flames burn hotter based on his emotional state
•	Unique trait: Can burn NON-PHYSICAL things 
o	Burns Resolve energy directly
o	Burns emotional connections (severs bonds)
o	Burns memories (from himself or others - dangerous)
Signature Moves:
•	"Cremation Zone" - Creates field where everything burns slowly
•	"Soul Pyre" - Direct flame attack on enemy's Core
•	"Ash Revival" - Burns his own injuries away (extreme pain, but effective healing)
Combat Style:
•	Mid-range fighter
•	Area denial specialist
•	Gets MORE dangerous the longer fight continues (battlefield becomes inferno)
•	Reckless with collateral damage
________________________________________
PERSONALITY:
•	Nihilistic but functional
•	"Everything burns eventually. I just speed up the process."
•	Chain smoker, heavy drinker
•	Gallows humor constantly
•	Surprisingly kind to civilians (harsh to combatants)
•	Quirk: Lights people's cigarettes with finger snap
Backstory Sketch:
•	Awakened Resolve during building fire (family died, he survived)
•	Blames himself (could've saved them if he'd awakened sooner)
•	Became Resolver to "burn away threats before they burn innocents"
•	The scars are self-inflicted (pushed his power too far trying to save someone)
Character Arc:
•	Starts suicidal (doesn't care if he dies in battle)
•	Tetsu's team shows him life worth living for
•	Final arc: Sacrifices himself with massive flame attack (burns out his Core)
•	Dies smiling: "Finally... warm."
Why He's Cool:
•	Black flames are VISUALLY SICK
•	Smoking aesthetic + fire powers = style
•	"Burns memories" ability is unique/terrifying
•	Self-destructive hero type (like Nanami but MORE tragic)
•	That asymmetrical eye + scar combo
