3. WEAPON MASTER - "ARSENAL"
BASIC INFO:
Name: KAEDE MURAMASA (村正 楓) Age: 24 Grade: 2 Affiliation: Resolver, specializes in anti-Ruptured operations
APPEARANCE:
•	Average height, muscular build (practical, not bulky)
•	Short black hair, always tied back
•	Covered in small scars (from weapon testing)
•	Wears tactical gear with MANY holsters/sheaths
•	Bandaged hands (constantly gripping weapons = calluses)
•	VISUAL HOOK: Weapons float around her in orbit (telekinetic-style)
RESOLVE MANIFESTATION: "ARMORY PROJECTION"
Conviction: "Every problem has a tool. I have them all."
How it works:
•	Can manifest ANY weapon she's touched/studied
•	Weapons are Resolve constructs (disperse when she dismisses them)
•	Limit: Can maintain 7 weapons simultaneously
•	Each weapon has properties of original (sharpness, weight, balance)
•	Unique trait: Can "combine" weapons mid-fight (sword + chain = chain-sword, etc.)
Her Arsenal (Favorites):
1.	Nodachi (long katana - main weapon)
2.	Kusarigama (chain-sickle - mid-range)
3.	Yumi bow (long-range)
4.	Tanto (close-range backup)
5.	Naginata (polearm for groups)
6.	Kanabo (heavy club - armor-breaking)
7.	Shuriken (throwables)
Signature Moves:
•	"Weapon Storm" - All 7 weapons attack independently
•	"Forge Cycle" - Dismisses weapons, summons new set instantly (adaptability)
•	"Fusion Armament" - Combines all 7 into one ultimate weapon (temporary, draining)
Combat Style:
•	Tactical weapons specialist
•	Analyzes enemy, selects perfect counter-weapon
•	Switches weapons mid-combo fluidly
•	Can fight 1v1 or 1v20 equally well
________________________________________
PERSONALITY:
•	Stoic, professional, weapon NERD
•	Talks about weapons like art (gets passionate about craftsmanship)
•	Quiet normally, won't shut up about blades
•	Collects antique weapons (studies them to add to arsenal)
•	Surprisingly gentle outside combat (likes tea ceremony, flower arrangement)
•	Quirk: Names all her weapons (talks to them)
Backstory Sketch:
•	Daughter of famous blacksmith family
•	Father made weapons for pre-Collision Naturals
•	Awakened Resolve when father was killed by Ruptured using his own blade
•	Vowed to master ALL weapons (so none can be used against her)
Relationship with Tetsu:
•	Mentor figure (teaches weapon fundamentals)
•	Respects his analytical mind
•	Tetsu: "How do you choose which weapon?"
•	Kaede: "The weapon chooses itself. You just have to listen."
Character Arc:
•	Starts believing weapons > people (tools are reliable, people aren't)
•	Learns teamwork through Division 7
•	Final battle: Breaks all 7 weapons to save teammate (chooses PEOPLE over tools)
Why She's Cool:
•	Floating weapon orbit is ICONIC visual
•	Weapon fusion gimmick is fresh
•	7-weapon limit creates strategy (which to use?)
•	Stoic weapon nerd personality is fun contrast
•	Female character who's just GOOD at fighting (no fanservice, pure skill)
