His body starts SMOKING (literally overheating).

Tetsu: "You're killing yourself—"

Raiden: "Better than being SLOW—"

Collapses. Seizure. Heart stops.

They revive him (Daichi + defibrillator).

Hospital for weeks.

Doctors: "Your nervous system is fried. One more Overdrive session could kill you."

Raiden: "...But I need it. I need to feel fast."

Tetsu: "You ARE fast. You don't need Overdrive to prove it."

Raiden: "Yes I do. Without it I'm just... normal. Boring. SLOW."

Tetsu: "Then be slow. Better slow than dead."

Raiden: "...I don't know how to be slow."
Recovery:
•	Forced break from combat (6 months)
•	Learns to function WITHOUT Overdrive
•	Discovers he's STILL Grade 1 without it (he forgot)
•	Overdrive becomes last resort, not default
•	Final form: "Controlled Storm" - uses Overdrive wisely, not constantly
