POWER EXPANSION - HOST'S ABILITIES:
You're right—we need MORE than just "sees future." Let's expand:
________________________________________
HOST'S RESOLVE: "PATHFINDER"
Core Ability: Foresight (3-5 second precognition)
But ALSO includes:
1. PREDICTION LINES (Visual Aid)
•	When active, silver lines appear in his vision
•	Shows trajectory of attacks, movement paths, consequence chains
•	Can share vision with allies (projects lines they can see too)
•	Combat use: Guides teammates through complex battles
2. PROBABILITY CALCULATION
•	Doesn't just see ONE future—sees MULTIPLE possible futures simultaneously
•	Can calculate success percentages
•	"This attack has 34% success rate. This one has 67%."
•	Weakness: Too many options = decision paralysis
3. CONSEQUENCE MAPPING (Signature Move)
•	Focuses on ONE decision deeply
•	Sees ripple effects beyond 5 seconds (up to 1 minute)
•	"If I do THIS, then THAT happens, which leads to..."
•	Cost: Extreme mental strain (nosebleeds, migraines)
•	Can only use 2-3 times per battle
4. TACTICAL ZONE
•	Creates a field around himself (10-meter radius)
•	Within zone: Allies gain slight precognition (0.5 seconds)
•	Enemies feel "watched" (instinctive unease)
•	Team support ability
5. COUNTER STANCE
•	Defensive technique using perfect prediction
•	Waits for attack, sees it coming, positions for PERFECT counter
•	Redirects enemy momentum against them
•	Weakness: Requires patience (Other hates this move)
6. FUTURE LOCK
•	Advanced technique (learns mid-story)
•	"Locks in" a specific future he's seen
•	For 3 seconds, that future MUST happen
•	Example: Sees ally dodging attack successfully → Locks that future → Ally automatically dodges even if they wouldn't have
•	Cost: Massive Resolve drain, can only use once per day
7. BLIND SPOT DETECTION
•	Passive ability (always on)
•	Senses attacks from behind/hidden threats
•	Can't be ambushed (sees the assassination attempt before it happens)
8. ANALYSIS OVERDRIVE (Desperation Move)
•	Pushes Foresight to 10 seconds (double normal)
•	Sees dozens of futures at once
•	Perfect for impossible situations
•	Cost: Afterwards, can't use Foresight for 10 minutes (vulnerable period)
________________________________________
