________________________________________
NEW RULE: EYE COLOR CHANGES ARE RARE
MOST Resolvers:
•	Eyes stay NORMAL when using powers
•	Resolve manifests through other means (auras, constructs, elements, etc.)
•	Eye changes are NOT standard
TETSU & AKA:
•	Eye color change is EXTREMELY RARE manifestation
•	Result of their unique dual-core split situation
•	Maybe only 0.1% of Resolvers have eye changes
•	Marks them as "special cases"
________________________________________
IMPLICATIONS:
For Civilians:
•	DON'T automatically know Tetsu/Aka are Resolvers from eyes alone
•	Might think: "Cool contacts?" "Genetic condition?" "Weird mutation?"
•	Only realize when they see POWERS being used
For Other Resolvers:
•	KNOW eye changes are significant
•	"Wait, your EYES changed? That's... that's not normal."
•	Marks them as unusual even among Resolvers
•	Other Resolvers are curious/wary about it
For Tetsu:
•	Can walk around with silver eyes and people just think he's "unique looking"
•	Sunglasses if he wants to hide it
•	Not immediately clocked as Resolver by everyone
For Aka:
•	Black eyes with red pupils look INTIMIDATING
•	People avoid him (think he's dangerous/weird)
•	But don't necessarily know he's a Resolver
•	Just think "that guy looks scary"
________________________________________
WHO WOULD RECOGNIZE THEM AS RESOLVERS:
✅ Other Resolvers (sense Resolve energy, not just eyes) ✅ Resolver organizations (database, files, surveillance) ✅ People who've seen them fight (witnessed powers + eyes) ❌ Random civilians (just think "weird eye color") ❌ Police/normal authorities (unless specifically told)
