•	Places invisible lightning "marks" on enemies/surfaces
•	Can detonate all marks simultaneously OR sequentially
•	Delayed trap system (mark now, trigger later)
•	Maximum 7 marks active
4. STORM FIELD
•	Creates electrified zone (10m radius)
•	Enemies inside take constant small damage
•	Allies' metal weapons get electric coating
5. CHAIN LIGHTNING
•	Lightning jumps between marked/wet targets
•	Efficient multi-target damage
•	Requires setup (marking or environmental water)
6. THUNDER STEP
•	Brief lightning-speed movement
•	Covers short distance instantly
•	Can only use 3 times per battle (stamina cost)
________________________________________
COMBAT STYLE:
•	Setup Fighter: Places wires/marks before engagement
•	Tactical Controller: Manipulates battlefield
•	Precision Striker: Calculated attacks on weak points
