Conviction: "I build fortresses that protect my people"
How it works:
•	Creates defensive structures from Resolve
•	Can manifest walls, barriers, bunkers
•	Also creates warrior constructs (autonomous defenders)
•	Strategic/defensive focus
________________________________________
ABILITIES:
1. SENTINEL WALL
•	Manifests solid barrier (any size/shape)
•	Can create multiple walls simultaneously
•	Walls last until destroyed or dismissed
•	Can reshape mid-battle
2. FORTRESS PROTOCOL
•	Creates complete defensive structure
•	Bunker-style shelter for team
•	Reinforced walls, protected interior
•	Can maintain for hours (Kurosawa Lineage stamina)
3. GUARDIAN CONSTRUCTS (Signature)
•	Manifests humanoid warrior constructs
•	Up to 3 active simultaneously
•	Each has basic combat AI (autonomous)
•	Follows orders but fights independently
•	Made of solid Resolve energy (silver-gray)
•	Kurosawa Lineage: Constructs last 2x longer than normal
4. ARTILLERY PLATFORM
•	Creates elevated position with protective walls
•	Gives ranged fighters advantage
•	Can launch Resolve projectiles from platform
5. MOBILE BARRIER
•	Shield that moves with user
•	Protects while advancing
•	Can extend to cover multiple people
6. EMERGENCY EXTRACTION
•	Encases wounded ally in protective shell
•	Immobilizes them but makes them invulnerable
•	Can roll/slide shell to safety
•	Emergency medic support
________________________________________
COMBAT STYLE:
•	Defensive Commander: Protects team, creates advantages
•	Strategic Leader: Positions constructs, directs team
•	Support Fighter: Enables others to excel
•	Last Line: Will hold position alone if needed
Weakness:
•	Offensive capabilities limited (few direct attacks)
•	Relies on team for damage output
•	Constructs can be overwhelmed by superior numbers
