TAKESHI KUROSAWA - SIMPLIFIED ABILITIES
Let me give you TWO options that are simple, dramatic, and GUT-HITTING cool.
________________________________________
OPTION 1: "MARKED GROUND"
Core Concept: Territory control through marking
How it works:
MARK (Setup):
•	Takeshi touches ground/surface
•	Leaves glowing mark (looks like tactical military symbol)
•	Can place up to 10 marks
•	Marks last until dismissed or he's knocked out
LOCKDOWN (Activation):
•	Connects all marks to create a ZONE
•	Within the zone: 
o	Allies: Can move freely, get slight buff
o	Enemies: Movement HEAVILY restricted (feels like walking through mud)
o	Effect: Harder enemies try to leave, harder it gets (like quicksand)
THE DRAMATIC MOMENT:
•	"This is MY ground now. You don't leave until I say so."
•	Last stand scenarios (hold position, buy time, protect someone)
•	Can make zones SMALLER to increase restriction (trade size for power)
Signature Move: "FINAL STAND"
•	Shrinks zone to just around himself (5m radius)
•	Enemies inside are COMPLETELY IMMOBILIZED
•	"If you want past me, you'll have to kill me first."
•	Can only use once per battle (costs everything)
Visual:
•	Glowing tactical marks on ground (gold/white)
•	Zone boundaries shimmer (like heat haze)
•	Enemies struggle against invisible force
•	Takeshi stands center, unmovable
________________________________________
OPTION 2: "LAST LINE" (Aura-based)
Core Concept: Becomes STRONGER the more desperate the situation
How it works:
RESOLVE AURA:
•	Takeshi emits golden aura
•	Aura strength tied to how BAD the situation is
•	Formula: More allies down/injured = Stronger he becomes
STAGES:
STAGE 1 - Full Team (Everyone healthy):
•	Normal power, no aura
•	Fights at base Grade 2 level
STAGE 2 - Team Injured:
•	Golden aura appears
•	1.5x power increase
•	"Don't worry. I've got this."
STAGE 3 - Team Critical:
•	Aura intensifies (bright gold, visible pressure)
•	2x power increase
•	Can fight multiple Grade 2s alone
STAGE 4 - Last Man Standing:
•	FINAL BULWARK activated
•	Aura EXPLODES (blinding gold, battlefield shakes)
•	3x power increase
•	Can fight Grade 1 temporarily
•	"I'm the last line. And last lines DON'T BREAK."
THE DRAMATIC MOMENTS:
•	Team watches him get STRONGER as they fall
•	"Captain, you're glowing—"
•	"I know. GET OUT OF HERE. NOW."
•	Solo last stands that buy time for escape
•	Self-sacrifice plays (stay behind while team runs)
Abilities within aura:
1.	GUARDIAN'S STAND 
o	Plants feet, becomes UNMOVABLE
o	Can't be pushed, thrown, or knocked down
o	"I'm not moving."
2.	PROTECTIVE FIELD 
o	Aura expands to shield area behind him
o	Enemies can't pass through without fighting him first
o	Literal "last line of defense"
3.	DESPERATE STRIKE 
o	Single devastating attack (all power into one hit)
o	Only available at Stage 4
o	Usually enough to take down one major threat
o	Exhausts him after
Visual:
•	Gold aura that intensifies with desperation
•	Eyes glow gold when aura active
•	Ground cracks under his feet (pressure)
•	Air HEAVY around him (oppressive presence)
