What made your story UNIQUE was:
•	ONE person split into TWO
•	Same origin, opposite philosophies
•	Internal conflict made external
•	"Who am I when I disagree with myself?"
If they were always two separate brothers:
•	It's just reincarnation (been done)
•	Loses the identity crisis element
•	Becomes "brothers reunited" not "self at war with self"
