ALTERNATIVE APPROACHES:
Let me offer some options that keep YOUR unique concept while addressing what the past-life idea might solve:
________________________________________
OPTION A: FRAGMENT INHERITANCE (Not Full Reincarnation)
The Concept:
•	The Fractured One (original fighter) HAD a brother
•	They fought together, died together in ancient battle
•	Their Resolve scattered across time
•	Tetsu inherited FRAGMENTS of both their souls
•	NOT full reincarnation (Tetsu is still Tetsu)
•	But carries ECHOES of the brothers
