YOUR VERSION:
✅ BOUND BY ANCIENT TECHNIQUE - not random chance ✅ PROTECTIVE CURSE - The Other returns ONLY when Tetsu is in danger ✅ FORCED PARTNERSHIP - Neither chose this, but have to deal with it ✅ PSYCHOLOGICAL HORROR - "My dead brother is inside my head" ✅ EXPLAINS SPECIFICITY - Why Tetsu? Because The Other CHOSE him 800 years ago ✅ TRAGIC IRONY - The Other wanted to protect Tetsu, but being inside him causes conflict
